HEADWORD: Cockswain
<hw>Cock"swain</hw> <pr>(?, <mark>colloq</mark>. ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Cock</ets> a boat + <ets>swain</ets>; hence, the master of a
boat.]</ety> <def>The steersman of a boat; a petty officer who has
charge of a boat and its crew.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

